Represents a meeting request 

| Element | Description | Type | Required | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
|meeting | New meeting request | meeting data object | Required | |
| &nbsp; &nbsp; time | When the meeting starts | string | Required | Format : YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM. Timezone is GMT.|
| &nbsp; &nbsp; duration | How long the meeting lasts | number | Required | In minutes |
| &nbsp; &nbsp; description | Description of the meeting | string | Required | |
| &nbsp; &nbsp; location | Location of the meeting | string | Optional | Default is an empty string |
| &nbsp; &nbsp; reminder | How many minutes before the meeting a reminder should take place | number | Optional | Default is 10 minutes |
| &nbsp; &nbsp; invitees | List of email addresses of people to invite to the meeting | array of string | Optional | The string should be a valid email address. Default is an empty array |